HELP:English/dasmphelp.guide
S:dasmphelp.guide

You can also set your own path + file or switch off the online help with 
tooltype @{"ONLINEHELP" link hotkeys,12}

If all these fail, no help file will be used. Which means nothing will 
happen if you press HELP button.

